# AUI Development Framework

- Treat `docs/use-cases/` as the source of behavioral intent.
- Keep Related Code sections current when implementation changes.
- Use `docs/templates/` when adding use cases, issue drafts, or decision records.
- Prefer portable repository-relative paths.
- Do not introduce absolute symlinks for shared code.
- Run `make check` before committing when available.

